# S06-T04: Performance Overlay

## Objective
Compact overlay showing FPS, GPU timing, memory, render budget, dropped frames, packet loss.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Top-right widget (toggleable in debug panel).
- Metrics: FPS (rAF interval EMA), heap (`performance.memory` if avail), render budget (`requestAnimationFrame` time), drops, WS latency.
- Visual color coding per threshold (UI_REGULATION palette).
- "PERFORMANCE MODE ACTIVE" banner when adaptive degradation triggers (S01-T08).

## Steps
1. Subscribe to `PerformanceManager` (S01-T08).
2. Render metrics in single-line monospace strip.
3. Add banner component for degraded mode.
4. Position above center video, height ≤ 24px.

## Invariants
- Overlay is read-only — never affects runtime decisions.
- Refresh at 2Hz max.
- Hidden by default in production.
